Significant changes have been made in this fork, including: a full package
refactor; genre management (audit/normalize/fill from TMDB/OMDb); Slavic
(SK/CZ) description and title localization with persistent caching; library
cleanup with rating-decay protection; missing-episode and franchise-gap
analysis; quality comparison; marimo analytics dashboards; a 1000+ test suite;
and CI/CD. See CHANGELOG.md for details.
